### Alerts

```html
<div class="alert alert-info">Informational text…</div>
<div class="alert alert-success">Success text…</div>
<div class="alert alert-warning">Warning text…</div>
<div class="alert alert-error">Error text…</div>
```

**Alert usage**

- Always include a clear title or leading phrase: “Couldn’t save changes”, “3 devices require attention”, etc.  
- For destructive or blocking errors, combine `alert-error` with an action (Retry, Download log, Contact support).  
- Avoid stacking more than one persistent alert per page; consolidate messages where possible.

